  "text": "To meet the challenges posed by appearance variations, one paradigm is to develop PR algorithms that are inherently robust against the changes. Methods under this paradigm attempt to extract the \"visual essence\" of a place that is independent of appearance changes [CITATION_1] . However, such methods have mostly been demonstrated on more \"natural\" variations such as time of day and seasons.",
